To solve this addition problem, we will add the numbers in base 6:

\[
\begin{array}{c@{}c@{}c@{}c@{}c}
& & & \text{4} & \text{5} & \text{3} & \text{0} & \text{0} & \text{0}_6 \\
& & + & \text{1} & \text{5} & \text{0} & \text{1} & \text{3} & \text{5}_6 \\ \cline{2-9}
& & & \text{5} & \text{0} & \text{3} & \text{1} & \text{3} & \text{5}_6 \\
\end{array}
\]

Therefore, $453000_{6} + 150135_{6} = 503135_{6}$.